[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0610","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0610.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0370","title":"Sun Solaris 与 SunOS man 及 catman 任意文件覆盖漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 和 SunOS 系统中的 man 与 catman 命令存在文件覆盖漏洞，本地攻击者可通过利用这些命令在处理临时文件时的缺陷，将任意文件写入目标系统上的指定路径，实现文件覆盖或权限提升。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 及 SunOS 多个版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限。厂商已发布相应安全补丁修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0370"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.047","remediation":"建议升级到 Sun 官方补丁对应的 Solaris 版本（如 Solaris 2.6 及更新版本已修复此问题），或从 sunsolve.sun.com 获取 man/catman 相关安全补丁。临时缓解措施：以 root 权限执行 `chmod 755 /usr/bin/man /usr/bin/catman` 移除 setuid 位，防止普通用户利用提权覆盖任意文件。同时通过 `tty` 访问控制限制本地用户登录高危账户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/165"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0610.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0585","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0585.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0353","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9107,\"outputTokens\":28,\"totalTokens\":10799}}","description":"HP-UX 系统中的 rpc.pcnfsd 服务存在权限配置错误漏洞，远程未经身份认证的攻击者可通过修改主打印机假脱机目录的权限，获取远程 root 权限访问。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重。攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，通过篡改打印机假脱机目录权限实现权限提升至 root 权限，严重威胁系统安全。建议升级至修复版本或禁用 rpc.pcnfsd 服务。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0353"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.860","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 到最新的Patched-Up 11.11 或更高版本，并应用最新的安全补丁包。具体步骤：1. 执行\"swinstall -s /somepath/hpus11v1_patch\"安装补丁；2. 检查并删除不必要的rpc.pcnfsd服务，使其处于禁用状态；3. 在防火墙上配置规则，仅允许本地网络段访问rpc.pcnfsd端口；4. 验证/spool目录的权限，确保持有者为root且权限为755，禁止其他用户修改。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-026.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9902-091","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0353.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0353","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0353.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0353.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2cv7-m7r7-5xxj/GHSA-2cv7-m7r7-5xxj.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/h/hpux_PHCO_14625.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0353.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/hpux_PHKL_15689.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x6000/5377/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0585.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0604","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0604.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0368","title":"WU-FTPD ProFTPD realpath 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"WU-FTPD 2.4.2、SCO Open Server 5.0.5 及 ProFTPd 1.2 pre1 等 FTP 服务器软件中的 realpath 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务发送特制的路径请求触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用此漏洞可在目标系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现完全控制服务器。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，且已有公开利用代码。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0368"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.780","remediation":"升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.6.2 及以上版本，或升级 ProFTPd 至 1.2.1 及以上版本。SCO Open Server 用户应安装最新补丁包或迁移至受支持的操作系统。如无法升级，在 inetd 配置中禁用 FTP 服务或使用 TCP Wrappers 限制访问来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0368","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19087","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7638326ff3f30ccdb52a67547408dd61f5cdc6cc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0368.json","https://github.com/REMath/implementations/blob/045b59dc77d5bd3e9a14713898ebcfdebacd11e9/tanalysis/tanalysis/verisec%20v1.0/wu-ftpd/CVE-1999-0368/README","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0368","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0368.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0368.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pjq9-4mrj-pv4g/GHSA-pjq9-4mrj-pv4g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/westtide/open-source-case-studies/blob/57e71842cdb3e034316b0d083f8d19f680501b67/verisec/.frama-c/programs_apps_wu-ftpd_CVE-1999-0368_realpath-linkpath_prefix_ok.eva/nonterm.log","https://github.com/tomhart-msc/verisec/blob/02f3a9660885181705e7550b8609534bbbaa414c/programs/apps/wu-ftpd/CVE-1999-0368/README","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0368.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0604.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0603","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0603.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0367","title":"NetBSD netstat 本地内核内存访问漏洞","description":"NetBSD 系统的 netstat 命令存在本地内核内存泄露漏洞。由于 netstat 工具在处理网络统计信息时未能正确限制对内核内存区域的访问权限，本地攻击者可通过执行特制的 netstat 命令读取内核敏感数据，导致内核信息泄露。该漏洞影响早期 NetBSD 版本，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限才能利用，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0367"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.657","remediation":"升级 NetBSD 至 1.4.1 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 NetBSD 1.4.1 的安全补丁中修复。如无法升级，可通过 chmod 700 /usr/bin/netstat 限制 netstat 命令的执行权限，仅允许 root 用户使用，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7571"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0603.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0648","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0648.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0407","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 /IISADMPWD 虚拟目录暴力破解密码代理漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 默认安装包含 /IISADMPWD 虚拟目录，该目录中的文件可被攻击者用作暴力破解密码攻击的代理，或用于识别系统中的有效用户账户，导致敏感信息泄露和未授权访问。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0407"],"sources":["cve","nvd"],"published":"1999-02-09","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"删除 /IISADMPWD 虚拟目录或限制其访问权限；升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本并使用最新 IIS。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T14:05:38.472358263+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91983486431506&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92000623021036&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0648.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0601","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0601.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0366","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 网络共享空密码认证绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 存在空密码认证绕过漏洞。由于系统在处理空 NT 哈希值时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过使用空密码直接访问目标系统的网络共享资源，无需提供有效凭据。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者利用此漏洞可获取共享文件及敏感数据的读取权限，危害程度较高。Microsoft 已在安全公告 MS99-004 中发布修复更新。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0366"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-08","updated":"1999-02-08","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-004 提供的修补程序（对应 KB 文章 Q214840），该补丁修正了 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 中 SAM 认证逻辑错误。如无法安装补丁，可禁用域控制器上来自 DOS/Windows 3.1/Windows for Workgroups/OS/2/Macintosh 客户端的密码更改功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0366.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0366","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0366.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0366.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5fcq-r7m3-pxf5/GHSA-5fcq-r7m3-pxf5.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0366.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e0b64613-6d45-4a3b-8434-c9c2ceedf571.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000517.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0601.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0578","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0578.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0350","title":"Rational Software ClearCase for Unix db_loader 条件竞争本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM Rational ClearCase for Unix 3.2 版本中的 db_loader 程序存在竞态条件漏洞。本地攻击者利用该程序在处理 SUID 位设置时的时序问题，通过精心构造的竞争条件操作，可在目标系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现本地权限提升。攻击者需要具备本地系统访问权限，且成功利用需满足特定的时序窗口条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0350"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-08","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到 IBM Rational ClearCase 的修复版本（3.2 之后的版本已修复此问题）。由于该产品已停止维护，建议迁移到受支持的配置管理解决方案，或在系统层面限制不可信用户对 db_loader 程序的执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0350","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0350"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0578.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1391","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1391.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1201","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/98 TCP/IP Chorus 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows 95/98 系统在将多个 TCP/IP 协议栈绑定到同一 MAC 地址时存在拒绝服务漏洞（即 TCP Chorusing 攻击）。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 ICMP Echo（ping）数据包，触发所有绑定的协议栈同时发送 ping 响应，导致网络流量被急剧放大，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 95/98 系统，利用方式简单，无需认证即可远程触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1201"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:56.067","remediation":"Windows 95/98 已停止支持，微软不再提供安全更新。建议立即升级到受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11）。如无法升级，缓解措施包括：(1) 避免将多个 TCP/IP 协议栈绑定到同一 MAC 地址；(2) 在网络防火墙或主机防火墙上过滤入站 ICMP Echo 请求，限制 ICMP 流量速率；(3) 禁用不必要的 TCP/IP 协议栈绑定。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91849617221319&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/225","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7542","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1201.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1201.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1201","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/115c94bd1da3cc18977d652d6e78c9f4a5dfc13b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1201.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1201.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f37077e857e7a28bab83d284c23299407fb1af7e/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4j42-4g6h-g8rv/GHSA-4j42-4g6h-g8rv.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1201.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/tcp_chorusing.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/225/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1391.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1373","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1373.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1169","title":"Flavio Veloso Nobo 1.2 UDP数据包拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Flavio Veloso Nobo 1.2 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送一系列大型 UDP 数据包，导致服务器进程崩溃，从而造成服务不可用。该攻击无需身份认证，攻击条件简单，仅需网络可达即可触发。受影响版本仅为 Nobo 1.2，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1169"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.033","remediation":"该漏洞影响 Flavio Veloso Nobo 1.2，该软件已停止维护，无官方补丁。建议立即迁移至其他受支持的替代软件以消除风险；如无法替换，可在网络边界防火墙（如 iptables）添加规则 `iptables -A INPUT -p udp --dport 8800 -m length --length 1000:65535 -j DROP` 限制大尺寸 UDP 数据包，并将 Nobo 绑定至内网非标准端口，避免暴露于公网。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12284","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1169.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1169","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1169.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1169.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mmg4-v63x-pg9v/GHSA-mmg4-v63x-pg9v.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1169.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000514.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/be7ad03fdf3a412f0fd57a25f1732dc0ecfb1cb3/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1373.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0599","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0599.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0365","title":"Metamail mailcap 条目未过滤 shell 元字符远程命令执行漏洞","description":"metamail 邮件处理工具包中存在 shell 元字符注入漏洞，在将邮件内容传递给 mailcap 条目处理时未对 shell 元字符进行正确引号转义，导致远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制邮件触发命令执行。攻击者利用该漏洞可在受害者系统上以当前用户权限执行任意命令，影响广泛部署 metamail 的 Unix/Linux 系统。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0365"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.403","remediation":"升级 metamail 至 2.7-9 或更高版本，该版本已对 mailcap 文件中的 shell 元字符进行正确转义处理。如无法升级，可临时移除或禁用系统中所有不可信来源的 mailcap 配置项，同时限制邮件客户端自动调用 metamail 处理附件。在 sendmail 环境下，建议禁用自动执行 mailcap 条目的功能，并审查 /etc/mailcap 及用户 ~/.mailcap 中的每条规则，确保不含未引用的 shell 元字符。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0365","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0365.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0365","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0365.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0365.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gmgp-r787-3hjp/GHSA-gmgp-r787-3hjp.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0365.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000513.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0365.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0599.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1277","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1277.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1453","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1728,\"inputTokens\":9070,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10817}}","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4 的 Internet WebBrowser ActiveX 控件存在安全缺陷，远程恶意网站运营者可在用户访问其网页时，利用该 ActiveX 对象调用剪贴板相关接口，在未经用户明确授权的情况下读取受害者系统剪贴板中的文本内容。该漏洞影响使用 Internet Explorer 4 浏览器并启用了 ActiveX 控件的 Windows 平台用户，攻击条件为受害者需主动访问攻击者控制的恶意网页。利用方式是通过网页中嵌入的脚本调用 WebBrowser 控件的剪贴板访问能力，从而窃取用户复制的敏感信息（如密码、账号等），造成用户隐私泄露。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1453"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:28.370","remediation":"升级至 Internet Explorer 5.0 或更高版本，或在 IE 安全设置中禁用\"对未标记为可安全执行脚本的 ActiveX 控件初始化并执行脚本\"选项。临时缓解：在\"Internet 选项 → 安全 → 自定义级别\"中将该项设为\"禁用\"或\"提示\"，防止恶意网站通过 WebBrowser ActiveX 对象读取剪贴板内容。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91979439932341&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/215","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19164","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe807f4098db5a5ad8dcb41a479197724cb9e789/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1453.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1453","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1453.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1453.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2h45-5j5p-4w53/GHSA-2h45-5j5p-4w53.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1453.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000512.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--3d9d1eb9-1f9f-40fa-b0d5-9c185e848ece.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1277.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1247","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1247.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1171","title":"Ipswitch WS_FTP Server 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Ipswitch IMail Server 5.0 及 WS_FTP Server 1.0.1/1.0.2 存在本地权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者可通过将注册表中 \"flags\" 键值设置为 1920，从而获取额外系统权限，进而修改或添加邮件账户。该漏洞需要攻击者拥有本地访问权限，利用门槛较低，可导致未授权账户操作和数据泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1171"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.283","remediation":"限制对注册表中 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Ipswitch\\WS_FTP\\flags` 键的写入权限，仅允许 Administrators 组访问。同时将 Ipswitch WS_FTP Server 升级至 2.0 及以上版本，或改用已停止支持的替代方案；对于 IMail Server，升级至 5.0 之后的安全版本并限制本地交互式登录用户范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91816507920544&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/218","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19167","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1171.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1171","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1171.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1171.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gpw9-cfwq-7rm5/GHSA-gpw9-cfwq-7rm5.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1171.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000511.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5f1126f3-181a-40e2-b8db-44c185a4cc5d.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1247.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0619","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0619.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0383","title":"ACC Tigris 未授权访问漏洞","description":"ACC Tigris 存在未授权访问漏洞，远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可直接访问系统管理界面，获取敏感信息或执行未授权操作。该漏洞影响 ACC Tigris 产品，攻击者只需网络可达即可利用，无需复杂攻击条件。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0383"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.773","remediation":"ACC Tigris 产品已停止维护，无官方补丁可用。建议立即在 Web 服务器前端部署反向代理（如 Nginx/Apache）并配置 HTTP 基本认证或 IP 白名单访问控制；同时在网络防火墙层面限制对 ACC Tigris 服务端口（默认 80）的访问来源，仅允许受信 IP 段连接。长期方案为迁移至受支持的现代 Web 服务器软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/267","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/183","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0383.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0383","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0383.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0383.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7hmx-xxrr-h2wg/GHSA-7hmx-xxrr-h2wg.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/account_public_public.nasl","https://github.com/LubyRuffy/plugins/blob/f873b19f27c95eaf2993ca4acde5cb7965d2ee3f/pre2008/acc.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0383.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0619.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0619.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0594","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0594.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0362","title":"Ipswitch WS_FTP Server 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Ipswitch WS_FTP Server 1.0.1 及 1.0.2 版本存在远程拒绝服务漏洞。未经身份认证的攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送特制的 CWD（Change Working Directory）命令，导致 FTP 服务进程异常崩溃或停止响应，从而中断正常的文件传输服务。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危，受影响用户应升级至更高版本以修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0362"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.990","remediation":"升级至 WS_FTP Server 1.0.3 及以上版本可修复此漏洞；在防火墙中限制 FTP 服务端口的访问来源 IP，防止未授权远程连接发起 CWD 命令攻击。鉴于该产品版本过于老旧，建议迁移至受支持的最新版 WS_FTP Server 或替代 FTP 服务软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD02021999.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/217","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0362","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0362.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/wsftp_cwd_dos.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/Ipswitch%20WS_FTP%20Server%20prior%205.0.2%20CWD%20path%20denial%20of%20service.plugin","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0594.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0595","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0595.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0363","title":"SuSE Linux 5.2 lpc 本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"S.u.S.E Linux 5.2 系统中的 lpc 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 lpc 程序发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 S.u.S.E Linux 5.2 版本，攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0363"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-02","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 SuSE Linux 至 5.3 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。临时缓解措施：移除 lpc 程序的 setuid 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/lpc），限制本地普通用户执行该程序。如非必要，可停止并禁用 lpd 打印服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/328","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19259"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0595.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0595.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0595.toml"}]